  <summary date="2024-04-25T18:22:11Z" status="Introduced in Senate">IMPACT to Save Moms Act

This bill requires the Centers for Medicare &amp; Medicaid Services to establish the Perinatal Care Alternative Payment Model Demonstration Project through FY2028 to allow states to test payment models for maternity care, including postpartum care, under Medicaid and the Children's Health Insurance Program (CHIP).&#160;</summary>
